item.title: CVE-2016-10519|2024-09-17T03:02:17.484Z -- hackerone -- bittorrent-dht%20node%20module
item.description: A security issue was found in bittorrent-dht before 5.1.3 that allows someone to send a specific series of messages to a listening peer and get it to reveal internal memory.
